This paper discusses the assessment of scientific journals from a bibliometric perspective, which is related to digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG) fields. The paper also mentions the differences in publication and citation behavior across disciplines, which is relevant to social and information networks (cs.SI) and cybersecurity (cs.CY) fields. Therefore, these five arXiv CS sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
